$Id$

INSTALL file for the DocBook Website distribution

----------------------------------------------------------------------
DTD installation
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Place the DTD files included in this distribution somewhere on
your system. Adjust your XML and SGML catalog(s), if appropriate,
such that they can find the included catalog.xml file.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
RELAX NG schema installation
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Place the *.rnc and *.rng files included in this distribution
somewhere on your system. Adjust your schema locating rules, if
appropriate, such that they can find the included
locatingrules.xml file.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
XSL stylesheet installation
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Place the XSL files in this distribution somewhere on your
system. Adjust your XML and SGML catalog(s), if appropriate, such
that they can find the included catalog.xml file.
